room_title: Escape room "The Lake House" by Psych Escape Room in Chicago
review: We did the Lake House - lots of fun. The clues were not too hard and not too easy. I have never done anything like this before but it was a great night out with friends.

room_title: Escape room "The Lake House" by Psych Escape Room in Chicago
review: This was our first escape room, so we did the Lake House (rated easiest of the three). We weren't sure what to expect, but we had a lot of fun & can't wait to go back to try another room!

room_title: Escape room "The Lake House" by Psych Escape Room in Chicago
review: The Lake House room was fantastic! We escaped with 2 minutes and 43 seconds. Highly recommended! That was a lot of fun.
